summary.description:
Today, cooler for the outside temperature (down 2.5°C) and feels like temperature (down 2.3°C), more moisture-laden outside humidity (up 10%), and drier conditions in rainfall (down 0.8 mm).

Compared to today, yesterday also had noticeable differences in cloud levels (up 707 m) and pressure (down 8 mbar).

The past week and month had observable variation in cloud levels (up 1150 m), feels like temperature (up 4.7°C), and outside temperature (up 3.6°C) when compared to today.
